      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,7 @@\n+created: 2026-01-04\n+title: Enhanced Documentation PR Workflow\n+intro: >-\n+  This release restores the `/docs:pr` command with enhanced cross-referencing capabilities\n+  that automatically link documentation PRs with parent project PRs. It also improves\n+  the synchronization workflow by automatically cloning the documentation repository\n+  when needed, eliminating manual setup steps."
